# 2026-03-04 23:47:45.083487
+## WHY
+We need a "League of 5" strategies to compete on ETH/USDT. We need to rank them based on their performance across 12 different market months.
+
+## WHAT
+
+Create user_data/strategies/league.json: This is the Scoreboard. It tracks: score, win_rate, and stagnation_count for 5 slots.
+
+Create scripts/league_manager.py: This script moves players up and down.
+
+If a Newbie beats a Prince, the Newbie becomes a Prince.
+
+If a Prince doesn't get better for 3 turns, kick him out and get a new AI Newbie.
+
+Create scripts/gauntlet.py: This script forces a bot to take 12 "Exams" (12 different months of ETH data).
+
+The Score formula: (Profit×SharpeRatio)/Drawdown.
+
+## HOW
+
+Use subprocess to run freqtrade backtesting.
+
+Use scripts/paths.py for all file paths.

# 2026-03-04 23:51:40.589302
+## WHY
+We are setting up a High-Performance Trading League for ETH/USDT. We need a scoreboard to manage 5 strategies through an evolutionary tournament.
+
+## WHAT
+
+Create user_data/strategies/league.json:
+Initialize 5 slots: champion, promising_1, promising_2, outsider_1, outsider_2.
+Each must track: score, total_profit, sharpe, drawdown, and stagnation_count.
+
+Create scripts/league_manager.py:
+
+Promotion Logic: If an outsider out-scores a promising, they swap. If a promising out-scores the champion, it becomes the new champion.
+
+Culling Logic: Each generation, if a bot doesn't improve its score, increment stagnation_count. At 3, reset the slot to empty for a new AI mutation.
+
+Create scripts/gauntlet.py:
+
+This script must run 12 backtests (one for each month of 2025) for a specific strategy using ETH/USDT 1m data.
+
+It must use python3 -m freqtrade backtesting.
+
+Calculation: Score=(Profit×Sharpe)/Drawdown.
+
+## HOW
+
+Use scripts/paths.py for all file resolution.
+
+Ensure gauntlet.py handles cases where a bot makes 0 trades (Score should be 0).
+
+Use subprocess with env={"PYTHONPATH": "."}.

